おいしい！ ヤバい！

142
00:09:47.837 --> 00:09:48.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実の笑い声）

143
00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:50.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（芽実）
史帆は肉食だもんね

144
00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:53.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（史帆）
え？ それ どういうこと？
もう！

145
00:09:53.884 --> 00:09:55.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（史帆）食べる？
（芽実）え？ いいの？

146
00:09:55.386 --> 00:09:57.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（芽実）
食べる　ありがとう

147
00:09:59.015 --> 00:10:00.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いただきます

148
00:10:02.351 --> 00:10:04.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
めっちゃ おいしい！

149
00:10:04.604 --> 00:10:06.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（史帆の笑い声）

150
00:10:07.189 --> 00:10:08.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（彩花）これだけ？

151
00:10:08.983 --> 00:10:09.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実）え？

152
00:10:10.568 --> 00:10:11.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん…

153
00:10:12.445 --> 00:10:15.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（彩花）史帆の声 久々に聞いた

154
00:10:16.824 --> 00:10:19.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（京子）
あれ？ いつから
しゃべんなくなったんだっけ？

155
00:10:20.077 --> 00:10:21.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
京子 スマホ　私も探してみる

156
00:10:22.496 --> 00:10:23.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）ああ

157
00:10:26.375 --> 00:10:27.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私もあった

158
00:10:32.089 --> 00:10:33.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（フォークで
グラスをたたく音）

159
00:10:34.508 --> 00:10:36.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（岡崎）
ちょっと あの…
みんな いいかな？

160
00:10:36.927 --> 00:10:37.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（久美）
何だろ？

161
00:10:39.764 --> 00:10:41.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
早く 食ってねえで

162
00:10:41.223 --> 00:10:42.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（岡崎）
美穂 ちょっと

163
00:10:44.727 --> 00:10:45.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
え〜と

164
00:10:47.772 --> 00:10:50.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
実は今日 ５月３日は

165
00:10:51.275 --> 00:10:53.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
僕と美穂が
交際を始めてから

166
00:10:53.944 --> 00:10:55.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
１周年記念日なんです

167
00:10:55.696 --> 00:10:57.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）フー！
（青年Ｂ）マジ？

168
00:10:57.990 --> 00:11:00.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（岡崎）
美穂
これからも よろしくね

169
00:11:01.827 --> 00:11:03.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（美玲）
おめでとう

170
00:11:03.371 --> 00:11:04.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年たち）おめでとう
（拍手）

171
00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:06.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（美穂）
ありがとう

172
00:11:07.041 --> 00:11:09.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（岡崎）
美穂
みんなのために笑って

173
00:11:11.545 --> 00:11:13.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
どうしたの？ 美穂
あんま元気ないけど

174
00:11:15.424 --> 00:11:17.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
あっ そうだ！ ほら
美穂の大好きな…

175
00:11:17.343 --> 00:11:18.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
ハンバーグあるけど
食べる？

176
00:11:19.887 --> 00:11:20.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
そっか…

177
00:11:21.347 --> 00:11:23.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）気取った野郎だな

178
00:11:23.599 --> 00:11:24.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（彩花）そういえば…

179
00:11:24.975 --> 00:11:28.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
親が船 持ってるって
聞いてもいないのに自慢された

180
00:11:28.270 --> 00:11:29.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）マジか…

181
00:11:29.313 --> 00:11:30.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ホント そういう男 ムリ

182
00:11:31.232 --> 00:11:32.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）私もムリだわ

183
00:11:32.733 --> 00:11:33.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（彩花）そもそも…

184
00:11:34.151 --> 00:11:36.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
なんで別荘に
行くことになったんだっけ？

185
00:11:36.404 --> 00:11:39.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（芽実）
確か 私たちに声かけたの
久美だったよね？

186
00:11:41.367 --> 00:11:43.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あのころ 美穂 落ち込んでたから…

187
00:11:44.412 --> 00:11:45.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そうだっけ？

188
00:11:47.373 --> 00:11:51.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
美穂と私の幼なじみが
亡くなったの

189
00:11:52.420 --> 00:11:54.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
幼なじみって…

190
00:11:54.839 --> 00:11:56.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
さっき言ってた…

191
00:11:57.091 --> 00:11:59.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（芽実）えっと…
（京子）マッシロ始めた人？

192
00:12:02.805 --> 00:12:05.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
私も聞いたときは
もちろんショックだった

193
00:12:06.392 --> 00:12:09.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
でも 美穂は
すごく落ち込んじゃってて…

194
00:12:09.979 --> 00:12:14.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
で 岡崎さんに相談して
美穂を元気づけようって…

195
00:12:21.073 --> 00:12:22.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（ざわめき）

196
00:12:22.241 --> 00:12:23.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
マジか？

197
00:12:35.212 --> 00:12:36.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（岡崎）
美穂

198
00:12:37.965 --> 00:12:39.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
僕は生涯…

199
00:12:39.967 --> 00:12:43.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
君を愛し続けることを
誓います

200
00:12:45.973 --> 00:12:48.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
う〜 おめでとう！

201
00:12:48.142 --> 00:12:50.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（拍手）

202
00:12:50.269 --> 00:12:51.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
それでは…

203
00:12:52.062 --> 00:12:53.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
未来の理事長に…

204
00:12:53.981 --> 00:12:55.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
乾杯！

205
00:12:55.608 --> 00:12:59.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（一同）
乾杯
おめでとう

206
00:12:59.528 --> 00:13:00.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
嫌みに感じない？

207
00:13:00.446 --> 00:13:01.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（彩花）
美穂 見して

208
00:13:02.406 --> 00:13:03.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
めっちゃ きれいだよ

209
00:13:04.533 --> 00:13:05.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ｂ）
スッゲえ きれい

210
00:13:06.035 --> 00:13:07.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（彩花）
すごい

211
00:13:08.037 --> 00:13:09.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ｃ）
俺も結婚したいな

212
00:13:09.205 --> 00:13:11.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（青年Ａ）
絶対 高かったろ？
ダイヤと金(きん)だ

213
00:13:18.589 --> 00:13:19.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（久美）だけど…

214
00:13:20.508 --> 00:13:24.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あの日のあと
美穂 もっと元気が なくなって…

215
00:13:24.428 --> 00:13:25.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ なんで？

216
00:13:25.971 --> 00:13:30.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（久美）
岡崎さんに“ほかに彼女が
いるんじゃないか”って言い始めて

217
00:13:30.351 --> 00:13:32.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
最低野郎だな

218
00:13:36.899 --> 00:13:37.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（美玲）ちょっといい？

219
00:13:39.818 --> 00:13:42.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
愛奈
さっきから なんで黙ってんの？

220
00:13:42.738 --> 00:13:43.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実）え？

221
00:13:45.282 --> 00:13:47.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お前 何 隠してんだよ！

222
00:13:48.077 --> 00:13:49.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
別に隠してない！

223
00:13:49.245 --> 00:13:50.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）じゃ 見せろよ

224
00:13:51.288 --> 00:13:52.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
変な言いがかりは やめてよ！

225
00:13:52.790 --> 00:13:53.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ いや…

226
00:13:54.375 --> 00:13:55.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実）どしたの？

227
00:13:56.001 --> 00:13:58.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
な… 何も隠してないから！

228
00:13:59.421 --> 00:14:02.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
何か ここから出れるヒントが
あるかもしれないから

229
00:14:02.967 --> 00:14:04.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ねっ 愛奈

230
00:14:04.718 --> 00:14:06.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私のスマホには何もなかった

231
00:14:08.264 --> 00:14:09.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ えっと…

232
00:14:10.391 --> 00:14:12.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ １枚あった！

233
00:14:12.226 --> 00:14:13.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
これ すっごい事実！

234
00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:15.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
ほら

235
00:14:15.688 --> 00:14:17.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
（京子）
これが
どうしたんだよ？

236
00:14:17.606 --> 00:14:19.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（愛奈）
この日の美玲 眼鏡しないで

237
00:14:19.275 --> 00:14:20.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
わざわざ
コンタクトしてきてたんだよ！

238
00:14:21.026 --> 00:14:21.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）はあ？

239
00:14:22.069 --> 00:14:23.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（久美）それが どうしたの？

240
00:14:23.571 --> 00:14:24.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（愛奈）いや この顔 見て！

241
00:14:25.072 --> 00:14:26.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
“ザ･女の子！”みたいな
顔してさ！

242
00:14:26.991 --> 00:14:29.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
違う！ その日は
たまたま眼鏡が壊れてて…

243
00:14:29.952 --> 00:14:31.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
知的な顔して 下心 見え見えで…

244
00:14:32.371 --> 00:14:33.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
っていうか それ
今 関係ないじゃん！

245
00:14:33.831 --> 00:14:35.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（愛奈）
美玲が言い始めたんでしょ！

246
00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:36.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ちょっと ２人とも…

247
00:14:37.209 --> 00:14:38.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（美玲）でもさ…
（愛奈）何よ？

248
00:14:38.878 --> 00:14:41.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（美玲）
あのときの愛奈 何か変だった

249
00:14:41.964 --> 00:14:43.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
は？ どこが？

250
00:14:44.008 --> 00:14:45.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ どういう意味？

251
00:14:45.467 --> 00:14:47.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何か 分からないけど

252
00:14:48.596 --> 00:14:52.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（愛奈）
ちょっと 美玲 やめて！
適当なこと言わないでよ！

253
00:14:52.600 --> 00:14:53.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
スマホ 見せてよ

254
00:14:53.559 --> 00:14:55.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ ちょっと 芽実！

255
00:14:55.144 --> 00:14:56.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（芽実）なに？
（愛奈）やめて！

256
00:14:56.228 --> 00:14:57.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
返して 返して！

257
00:14:57.605 --> 00:14:59.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（芽実）ちょっと 痛い 痛い！

258
00:14:59.648 --> 00:15:00.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
痛いってば

259
00:15:02.151 --> 00:15:03.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（愛奈）ごめん
（芽実）痛…

260
00:15:03.861 --> 00:15:05.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
愛奈 どうしたの？

261
00:15:05.988 --> 00:15:07.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
なんで そんなに興奮してんの？

262
00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:10.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
岡崎の浮気相手って お前か！

263
00:15:10.868 --> 00:15:13.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
違う 違う それは違う！

264
00:15:13.245 --> 00:15:14.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（美玲）ちょっと待って

265
00:15:14.830 --> 00:15:16.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何か いろいろ思い出してきた

266
00:15:18.083 --> 00:15:19.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（美玲）あの日の帰り…
（彩花）そうだ

267
00:15:20.210 --> 00:15:21.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
バスが来る時間なのに

268
00:15:22.046 --> 00:15:23.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
愛奈と岡崎さんだけ
見当たらなくて

269
00:15:23.923 --> 00:15:24.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
やめて！

270
00:15:24.965 --> 00:15:26.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京子）思い出した

271
00:15:26.634 --> 00:15:28.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そしたら
愛奈と岡崎が遅れてきたんだ

272
00:15:28.427 --> 00:15:29.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それは違う！

273
00:15:30.137 --> 00:15:32.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お前 まさか…

274
00:15:32.264 --> 00:15:33.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え… うそでしょ？

275
00:15:34.308 --> 00:15:35.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何もしてない！

276
00:15:35.726 --> 00:15:37.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
芽実 親友でしょ

277
00:15:37.728 --> 00:15:39.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お願い 助けて！

278
00:15:40.314 --> 00:15:41.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そういえば…

279
00:15:43.442 --> 00:15:46.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あのときの愛奈の顔
